{"tid":1056251,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"人民幣定期存款七日　利息5.5厘","createTime":"2019-03-11T05:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:03:35.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c62cf93b00162ac16a1ac85f4de6d4b036d4f3f9","tid":1056251,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:22:47.000Z","msg":"定期存款七日，利息有5.5厘，說的是人民幣定期存款，起存額為等值5萬港元之人民幣，由中銀香港提供。若資金較多，以等值20萬港元的人民幣計，定期存款一個月，利息則以花旗銀行提供的最高，利息高達6厘。<br />\n<br />\n投資界預計，熱錢於短期內會湧入美元，人民幣料短暫見頂，料本港銀行未來需逆市加息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/40evHJM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F40evHJM.png&h=4f0f001f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://wealth.hket.com/article/2290060/%E6%9B%BE%E6%A1%82%E8%8A%AC%20-%20%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%97%A5%E3%80%80%E5%88%A9%E6%81%AF5.5%E5%8E%98?r=cpsdlc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwealth.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2290060%2F%25E6%259B%25BE%25E6%25A1%2582%25E8%258A%25AC%2520-%2520%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%259C%259F%25E5%25AD%2598%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E4%25B8%2583%25E6%2597%25A5%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2581%25AF5.5%25E5%258E%2598%3Fr%3Dcpsdlc&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FANVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=15b80a68\" target=\"_blank\">https://wealth.hket.com/article/2290060/%E6%9B%BE%E6%A1%82%E8%8A%AC%20-%20%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE%E4%B8%83%E6%97%A5%E3%80%80%E5%88%A9%E6%81%AF5.5%E5%8E%98?r=cpsdlc</a>"},{"pid":"af5f7f45248d99c6085c19b27b5286ba6da2be5c","tid":1056251,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賺息蝕價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202f7ba733858903aa31b54faf5609f0e89054e2","tid":1056251,"uid":43483,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRio2LB.png\" data-t